item.description:
Hi Trailblazers, come out and listen to some great bands playing the best bluegrass music! We will be sitting behind the "Governors Inn Cafe" that's where the band plays! 

Bring a lawn chair because all the other seats fill up fast there. You  can order something to eat or drink something cold and refreshing.

We will be meeting there around 4 pm every Sunday for a different band playing "Bluegrass Music" This is a free event! If you get restless there is volleyball or horseshoe games to play!

If anyone gets lost or just wants to talk to me, my number is: 603-312-6735

See everyone there!

Peter
